00060 static int
00061 lustre_dissect_element_ldlm_lock_flags(
00062         tvbuff_t *tvb _U_, int offset _U_, packet_info *pinfo _U_,
00063         proto_tree *parent_tree _U_, int hf_index _U_)
00064 {
00065   proto_item *item = NULL;
00066   proto_tree *tree = NULL;
00067 
00068   if (parent_tree) {
00069     item = proto_tree_add_item(parent_tree,hf_index, tvb, offset, 4, TRUE);
00070     tree = proto_item_add_subtree(item, ett_lustre_ldlm_lock_flags);
00071   }
00072   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_lock_changed);
00073   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_block_granted);
00074   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_block_conv);
00075   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_block_wait);
00076   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_ast_sent);
00077   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_replay);
00078   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_intent_only);
00079   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_has_intent);
00080   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_flock_deadlock);
00081   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_discard_data);
00082   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_no_timeout);
00083   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_block_nowait);
00084   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_test_lock);
00085   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_cancel_on_block);
00086   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_cos_incompat);
00087   dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_deny_on_contention);
00088   return
00089     dissect_uint32(tvb, offset, pinfo, tree, hf_lustre_ldlm_fl_ast_discard_data);
